import React, { useState } from 'react'
import { Text, View, StyleSheet, ImageBackground } from "react-native"
import TextBox from "../components/TextBox"
import Btn from "../components/Btn"


const styles = StyleSheet.create({
    view: {
        flex: 1,
        width: "100%",
        justifyContent: "flex-end",
        alignItems: "center"
    },

    buttons: {

        height: 42,
        width: "82%",
        borderRadius: 25,
        marginTop: -25,
        marginBottom:"10%",
        backgroundColor: "#4D1A70",
        justifyContent: "center",
        alignItems: "center",
    },
    image: {
        flex: 1,
        justifyContent: "center"
      },
})



export default function Inicioscreen({ navigation}) {


    return <View  style={styles.view}>
        <ImageBackground source={require('../Img/fondo_inicio.png')} resizeMode="cover" style={styles.image}>

        
        <Btn onClick={() => navigation.navigate("Sign Up")} title="Registrarse ahora" style={styles.buttons} /> 
        <Btn onClick={() => navigation.navigate("Login")} title="Iniciar Sesion" style={styles.buttons} /> 

        </ImageBackground>
    </View>


}
